zeus.actors
Class ProducedDb

java.lang.Object
  zeus.actors.ProducedDb
public class ProducedDb
extends java.lang.Object

The Produced Resources Database is an internal storage component used by the Planner in the course of its activities. It is unlikely that developers will need to call these methods directly.
